Articles.Content:
Im going into parts in both hangars in there are non there please help

 

Edited February 27, 2016 by Maxf52

Please be more specific.

Are you playing career? If so, are you just not seeing very many parts, or none at all? At the beginning of science and career mode there are not very many parts available. 

Do you have any mods installed? Sometimes mods don't get along and bad things happen. 

Has it been working before and just now is a problem, or is this the first time you've tried to play?

Have you recently removed any mods? If you were deleting mod folders from the Game Data folder, it's possible you accidentally also deleted the Squad folder, which is where all the parts files are. 

This sounds more like a technical support question rather than gameplay, but still, a screenshot or two might help.
